This software uses the following third-party data and resources:

Astronomical Data:
- NASA JPL Ephemeris Data (DE440, JUP365, SAT441, NEP097)
  Source: NASA Jet Propulsion Laboratory
  https://ssd.jpl.nasa.gov/

- ESA Gaia Mission Data Release 3 (DR3)
  Source: European Space Agency
  https://www.cosmos.esa.int/web/gaia

- McConnachie (2012) Local Group Catalog
  Source: Astronomical Journal

- Karachentsev et al. (2013) Nearby Galaxies Catalog
  Source: Astronomical Journal

- 2MASS Redshift Survey (2MRS)
  Source: 2MASS Project

- Cosmicflows-3 Dataset
  Source: Tully et al. (2016)

Visual Resources:
- Planetary Textures
  Source: Solar System Scope
  https://www.solarsystemscope.com/textures/

- Galaxy Images
  Source: ESA/Gaia
  https://www.esa.int/ESA_Multimedia/Images

Satellite Data:
- Two-Line Element (TLE) Data
  Source: CelesTrak (NORAD)
  https://celestrak.org/

- UCS Satellite Database
  Source: Union of Concerned Scientists
  https://www.ucsusa.org/resources/satellite-database

